TDDB27 Project Specifications 
=================================
Functional Specifications 
=================================
This project will cover the functionality of any common web mail client. The client will cover mail writing, receiving and sending from a client mail account. The client will include design functionalities such as row-highlighting and customization. 

Technological Specifications 
=================================

The project will be using CodeIgniter for the server framework and Angular.js for the client framwork.
The project will use mySQL or similar SQL-type server data storage.
The project will probably use Oauth for the authentication process for the webpage, it would, however, be fun to see if the webpage could integrate with live gmail-accounts, or similar. The main goal is though to have our own system for emailing.